import React from 'react'
import Footer from '../components/Footer'

export function FooterContainer() {
    return (
        <Footer>
            <Footer.Wrapper>
            <Footer.Row>
                <Footer.Column>
                <Footer.Title>BlockChain</Footer.Title>
                <Footer.Link href="#">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Fusce eros arcu, pretium sollicitudin elit vel, luctus interdum nisi.</Footer.Link>
                </Footer.Column>
                <Footer.Column>
                <Footer.Title>Tentang Kami</Footer.Title>
                    <Footer.Link href="#">Layanan</Footer.Link>
                    <Footer.Link href="#">Tim Kami</Footer.Link>
                    <Footer.Link href="#">Berita</Footer.Link>
                </Footer.Column>
                <Footer.Column>
                <Footer.Title>Bantuan</Footer.Title>
                    <Footer.Link href="#">Customer Service</Footer.Link>
                    <Footer.Link href="#">Akun</Footer.Link>
                    <Footer.Link href="#">Feedback</Footer.Link>
                    <Footer.Link href="#">Aksebilitas</Footer.Link>
                </Footer.Column>
                <Footer.Column>
                <Footer.Text>Berlangganan dengan kami dan dapatkan informasi terbaru</Footer.Text>
                <form>
                    <Footer.Input>
                    <input id="email" type="email" placeholder='email' onChange={()=>doSomething} />
                    </Footer.Input>
                <Footer.Button type="berlangganan">Berlangganan</Footer.Button>
                </form>
                </Footer.Column>
            </Footer.Row>
            </Footer.Wrapper>
        </Footer>
    )
}
